Dialogue: 1,0:01:24.40,0:01:27.50,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\bord1\blur5\3a&H7E&}淚水根本不適合妳吧
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.90,0:01:31.89,OP_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\3c&H25A2F2&\blur5\3a&H24&\bord2}鏡子裡真正的我
